<h1 class="">Welcome to Ki Charter Academy</h1>
        <p class="">Welcome to Ki Charter Academy! We are a public charter school in San Marcos, Texas, that serves first through twelfth grade students with behavioral, academic, and developmental needs. Through our partnerships with the <a href="https://sanmarcostc.com/" title="" alt="" target="_blank">San Marcos Treatment Center</a>, <a href="https://www.sanmarcostx.gov/" title="" alt="" target="_blank">the city of San Marcos</a>, and <a href="https://www.txstate.edu/" title="" alt="" target="_blank" class="">Texas State University</a>, Ki Charter students develop the skills they need to become active citizens in their communities.</p>
        <h2 class="">A Message from Our Superintendent</h2>
        <p class="">Dear Community,</p>
<p class="">It is my honor to serve the students and families of Ki Charter. During this critical juncture in their lives, I hope you will find your partnership with Ki to be a lifeline of hope and a foundation for your child’s success. We know there will be challenges and growth opportunities for us all, but you have my promise that we will be completely transparent. Our students are at the forefront of everything we do. </p>
<p class="">Our teachers and staff work tirelessly advocating for their students both in and beyond the classroom. We strive to ensure that each student has the care and support needed to learn and grow while creating a cohesive and collaborative learning environment for all. We are fervently committed to reintroducing our students to their respective schools with improved behavior, reduced learning gaps, and the social-emotional skills to succeed. </p>
<p class="">Thank you for entrusting your child(ren) to us. Please do not hesitate to <a href="/Contact-Us" title="" alt="" target="_self">contact us</a> with your questions or concerns. We look forward to serving you.</p>
